Fermions coupled to a Constant Skyrme Field 

We are interested in the behaviour of fermions in the presence of a
background Skyrmion. 
The Skyrmion introduces a space-dependent
complex mass for the fermions. Therefore, it is instructive to
consider first a massive fermion on . 
This corresponds to  so that the fermion mass is
