The simplest method for obtaining a Skyrmion with baryon number 
is the ansatz . For  this Skyrme configuration has
very high energy. However, we are mainly interested in the interplay of topology
and the spectrum of the Dirac equation which should be independent of
the precise form of the Skyrmion.



